Class Club

  • java.lang.Object
    • Club

  • public class Club
extends java.lang.Object
    The Club class holds information about all climbers. It includes methods to return the climber who has recorded the highest average mountain height; the highest mountain climbed by a member of the club; and a list of all mountains that have been climbed that are higher than a given level.
    Version:
    26/10/2017
    Author:
    Susannce Christensen

      • searchClimber

        public Climber searchClimber(java.lang.String searchClimber)
        This method takes a String as a parameter. It then searches through all the climbers of the club to check for a match. If no match is found it will return null.
        Parameters:
        searchClimber - The search String.
        Returns:
        The climber match. Or null if no match.
